T e n t o r i u m. Anterior tentorial arm (“Ata” in 
Fig.4B - D
) originated from endoskeletal structure of antennal socket; anterior tentorial pit apparently located on medioventral wall of antennal socket (“Atp” in 
Fig. 4A - B
). Buttress-like extension absent. Internal plate (“Ip” in 
Fig.4B, D
