Fig.9K
); distiventral edge of the shaft produced to form broad lamina (arrow in 
Fig. 9H
). Lancet (gonapophysis VIII; = first valvula; “Lc” in 
Fig.9L
) completely lacks valves, with 5 apical barbs of which basal three are conspicuously large and directed ventrad, and apical two are small and inconspicuous.

